import React from "react";
import Chart from '../Chart/Chart'

const ExpenseChart=(props)=>{
    const chartDataPoints=[
        {label:'Jan',value:0},
        {label:'Feb',value:0},
        {label:'Mar',value:0},
        {label:'Apr',value:0},
        {label:'May',value:0},
        {label:'Jun',value:0},
        {label:'Jul',value:0},
        {label:'Aus',value:0},
        {label:'Sep',value:0},
        {label:'Oct',value:0},
        {label:'Nov',value:0},
        {label:'Dec',value:0},
    ]

    

    return (
        <Chart dataPoints={chartDataPoints}></Chart>
    )
}

export default ExpenseChart
